verbose_text: One clue comes from both S1P-S1PR2 and End1-Ednra being critical in the patterning of the ventral pharyngeal arch, which agrees with our demonstrating that Ednra, a possible downstream target of the Spns2-S1PR2 axis, synergizes with fibronectin to promote the lower jaw development.
evidence: Ednra, a possible downstream target of the Spns2-S1PR2 axis, synergizes with fibronectin
